"href":"/us/stat/71/441"},"text":"71 Stat. 441","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 10 (§ 451 et seq.) of Title 21, Food and Drugs. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s451"},"text":"section 451 of Title 21","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Egg Products Inspection Act, referred to in subsec. (c)(2), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/597"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–597","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-12-29"},"text":"Dec. 29, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/1620"},"text":"84 Stat. 1620","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to chapter 15 (§ 1031 et seq.) of Title 21, Food and Drugs. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t21/s1031"},"text":"section 1031 of Title 21","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
